'''Paladin''' was a term that referred to some kind of knight.

Paladins of the [[Knights of Zakuul]] were elite units who wore black armor rather than the gold of normal Zakuul Knights.<ref name="TOR">{{TORcite|exp=kotfe|type=flashpoint|The Star Fortress}}</ref>

